The **HDFS Toolkit** for **Bluemix** is a fork of the [HDFS toolkit](https://github.com/IBMStreams/streamsx.hbase).
The purpose of this fork is to enhance the existing operators to also support interacting with HDFS the BigInsights service in Bluemix. 

Integrating HBase and Bluemix

Use the com.ibm.streamsx.hbase.bluemix toolkit for connecting Streams applications to HBase servers running on the BigInsights for Bluemix service. It is available on the bluemix branch. Download the latest release.


Download the latest releaes of the HDFS Toolkit for Bluemix supporting Streams v4.1 and BigInsights version 4.0:
* [Bluemix Release](https://github.com/IBMStreams/streamsx.hbase/releases/tag/3.5.1-bluemix)

## Getting started with development:
 
* See the [sample](https://github.com/IBMStreams/streamsx.hbase/tree/bluemix/samples/HDFSBluemixDemo) for usage examples.


